-plaintiff-0606fd0d81a7\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-0606fd0d81a7.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Contemporaneous reporting on the status of U.S.-Iran talks immediately before the June 15, 2025 cutoff, including quoted Iranian foreign-ministry position and the scheduled sixth round in Oman.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T17:00:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"0606fd0d81a781db5b748a887348cc0d34980db7d174e5bdf37153846b0ca30a\",\"size_bytes\":2314,\"source_description\":\"Al Jazeera English article; extracted relevant page text from web retrieval.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/6/14/iran-says-nuclear-talks-with-us-meaningless-as-trump-pushes-for-a-deal\",\"storage_name\":\"06/0606fd0d81a781db5b748a887348cc0d34980db7d174e5bdf37153846b0ca30a\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Al Jazeera report: June 14, 2025 Iran cancels next US nuclear talks amid Israeli attacks\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T16:58:03Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_75f22524b70e_submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-75f22524b70e\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-75f22524b70e.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Later official U.S. government characterization of June 2025 events, directly bearing on whether the U.S. position was that Iran had refused to reach a deal rather than agreed to permanent peace by the cutoff.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T17:00:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"75f22524b70e48b6e0c7411de9b525197ca3501edd37e9a0646432f4fe887520\",\"size_bytes\":2022,\"source_description\":\"White House fact sheet; extracted page text from web retrieval.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/fact-sheets/2026/02/fact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-addresses-threats-to-the-united-states-by-the-government-of-iran/\",\"stor